<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Facture #{{ vente.id }}</title>
    <style>
        :root{
            --primary:#0f4c81;
            --dark:#1f2937;
            --muted:#6b7280;
            --line:#d1d5db;
            --soft:#f8fafc;
            --white:#ffffff;
        }

        *{
            box-sizing:border-box;
        }

        html, body{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size:11px;
            color:var(--dark);
            background:#eef2f7;
        }

        .sheet{
            width:148mm;
            min-height:210mm;
            margin:10px auto;
            background:var(--white);
            border:1px solid #e5e7eb;
            box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
            overflow:hidden;
        }

        .top-bar{
            height:6px;
            background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), #1d7bb8);
        }

        .page{
            padding:10mm 9mm 8mm 9mm;
        }

        .header{
            display:flex;
            justify-content:space-between;
            align-items:flex-start;
            gap:10px;
            border-bottom:1.5px solid var(--line);
            padding-bottom:8px;
            margin-bottom:8px;
        }

        .clinic{
            flex:1;
        }

        .clinic h1{
            margin:0 0 4px 0;
            font-size:16px;
            line-height:1.15;
            color:var(--primary);
            font-weight:800;
            text-transform:uppercase;
        }

        .clinic .sub{
            font-size:10px;
            color:var(--muted);
            margin-bottom:4px;
        }

        .clinic div{
            margin:1px 0;
            line-height:1.25;
        }

        .invoice-box{
            width:38mm;
            border:1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius:8px;
            padding:6px;
            text-align:center;
            background:var(--soft);
        }

        .invoice-box .title{
            font-size:14px;
            font-weight:800;
            color:var(--primary);
            margin-bottom:4px;
            text-transform:uppercase;
        }

        .invoice-box .ref{
            font-size:11px;
            font-weight:700;
        }

        .meta{
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
            gap:8px;
            margin-bottom:8px;
        }

        .box{
            border:1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius:8px;
            padding:7px 8px;
            background:#fff;
        }

        .box h3{
            margin:0 0 5px 0;
            font-size:11px;
            color:var(--primary);
            border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding-bottom:3px;
            text-transform:uppercase;
        }

        .box p{
            margin:3px 0;
            line-height:1.3;
        }

        .label{
            color:var(--muted);
            font-weight:700;
        }

        .table-wrap{
            border:1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius:8px;
            overflow:hidden;
            margin-bottom:8px;
        }

        table{
            width:100%;
            border-collapse:collapse;
        }

        thead th{
            background:var(--primary);
            color:#fff;
            font-size:10px;
            font-weight:700;
            padding:7px 5px;
            text-align:left;
        }

        tbody td{
            padding:6px 5px;
            border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;
            vertical-align:top;
            font-size:10.5px;
        }

        tbody tr:nth-child(even){
            background:#fafafa;
        }

        tbody tr:last-child td{
            border-bottom:none;
        }

        .center{text-align:center;}
        .right{text-align:right;}

        .bottom{
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:1fr 42mm;
            gap:8px;
            align-items:start;
            margin-bottom:8px;
        }

        .notes{
            border:1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius:8px;
            padding:7px 8px;
            min-height:60px;
            background:#fcfcfc;
        }

        .notes h3{
            margin:0 0 5px 0;
            font-size:11px;
            color:var(--primary);
            text-transform:uppercase;
        }

        .notes p{
            margin:3px 0;
            line-height:1.35;
            font-size:10px;
        }

        .totals{
            border:1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius:8px;
            overflow:hidden;
        }

        .totals th,
        .totals td{
            padding:7px 8px;
            border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;
            font-size:10.5px;
        }

        .totals tr:last-child th,
        .totals tr:last-child td{
            border-bottom:none;
        }

        .grand-total th,
        .grand-total td{
            background:var(--primary);
            color:#fff;
            font-size:12px;
            font-weight:800;
        }

        .footer{
            display:flex;
            justify-content:space-between;
            gap:10px;
            align-items:flex-end;
            border-top:1px dashed var(--line);
            padding-top:8px;
        }

        .footer-left{
            flex:1;
            font-size:9.5px;
            color:var(--muted);
            line-height:1.35;
        }

        .footer-right{
            display:flex;
            align-items:flex-end;
            gap:8px;
        }

        .qr{
            text-align:center;
            width:32mm;
        }

        .qr img{
            width:28mm;
            height:28mm;
            object-fit:contain;
            border:1px solid var(--line);
            padding:2px;
            border-radius:6px;
            background:#fff;
        }

        .qr small{
            display:block;
            margin-top:3px;
            font-size:8.5px;
            color:var(--muted);
            word-break:break-word;
            line-height:1.2;
        }

        .sign{
            width:35mm;
            text-align:center;
            font-size:9px;
            color:var(--muted);
        }

        .sign-line{
            margin-top:20px;
            border-top:1px solid #000;
            padding-top:3px;
        }

        .print-actions{
            text-align:center;
            padding:8px 0 12px;
            border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;
            background:#fafafa;
        }

        .btn-print{
            border:none;
            background:var(--primary);
            color:#fff;
            padding:8px 16px;
            border-radius:7px;
            font-size:11px;
            font-weight:700;
            cursor:pointer;
        }

        a{
            color:var(--primary);
            text-decoration:none;
        }

        @page{
            size:A5 portrait;
            margin:8mm;
        }

        @media print{
            html, body{
                background:#fff;
            }

            .sheet{
                width:100%;
                min-height:auto;
                margin:0;
                border:none;
                box-shadow:none;
            }

            .page{
                padding:0;
            }

            .print-actions{
                display:none !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="sheet">
    <div class="top-bar"></div>

    <div class="page">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="clinic">
                <h1>Clinique Médicale Nassarawa</h1>
                <div class="sub">Facturation / Caisse</div>
                <div><strong>NIF :</strong> 120402/R</div>
                <div><strong>RCCM :</strong> NE-NIM-01-2024-B12-00145</div>
                <div><strong>Adresse :</strong> Yantala Haut, Avenue du Daoura YN 187, Niamey</div>
                <div><strong>Tél :</strong> 20 75 51 02 / 88 05 22 20</div>
                <div><strong>BP :</strong> 2120 Niamey</div>
                <div><strong>Email :</strong> nassrawaclinique@gmail.com</div>
            </div>

            <div class="invoice-box">
                <div class="title">Facture</div>
                <div class="ref">N° {{ vente.id }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="meta">
            <div class="box">
                <h3>Informations</h3>
                <p><span class="label">Référence :</span> FACT-{{ vente.id }}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Date :</span> {{ vente.date ? vente.date|date('d/m/Y H:i') : '–' }}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Vendeur :</span>
                    {{ vente.vendeur ? vente.vendeur.nomComplet|default(vente.vendeur.getUserIdentifier ? vente.vendeur.getUserIdentifier() : '-') : '-' }}
                </p>
                <p><span class="label">Nature :</span> Vente pharmacie</p>
            </div>

            <div class="box">
                <h3>Client / Patient</h3>
                <p><span class="label">Nom :</span> {{ vente.patient.nomComplet ?? vente.patient.nom ?? 'Patient non renseigné' }}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Téléphone :</span> {{ vente.patient.telephone ?? '–' }}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Adresse :</span> {{ vente.patient.adresse ?? '–' }}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Observation :</span> Achat de médicaments</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="table-wrap">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th style="width:8%;">#</th>
                        <th style="width:42%;">Produit</th>
                        <th style="width:12%;" class="center">Qté</th>
                        <th style="width:18%;" class="right">PU</th>
                        <th style="width:20%;" class="right">Total</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                {% for ligne in vente.lignes %}
                    <tr>
                        <td class="center">{{ loop.index }}</td>
                        <td>
                            {{ ligne.medicament.nom }}
                            {% if ligne.medicament.codeBarre is defined and ligne.medicament.codeBarre %}
                                <br><small style="color:#6b7280;">CB : {{ ligne.medicament.codeBarre }}</small>
                            {% endif %}
                        </td>
                        <td class="center">{{ ligne.quantite }}</td>
                        <td class="right">{{ ligne.prixUnitaire|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }}</td>
                        <td class="right"><strong>{{ ligne.sousTotal|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }}</strong></td>
                    </tr>
                {% else %}
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="5" class="center">Aucune ligne enregistrée</td>
                    </tr>
                {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="bottom">
            <div class="notes">
                <h3>Notes</h3>
                <p>Merci pour votre confiance.</p>
                <p>Cette facture constitue une pièce justificative de vente.</p>
                <p>Médicaments ni repris ni échangés après livraison, sauf disposition particulière.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="totals">
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Sous-total</th>
                        <td class="right">{{ vente.total|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} FCFA</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Remise</th>
                        <td class="right">0 FCFA</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="grand-total">
                        <th>Total</th>
                        <td class="right">{{ vente.total|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} FCFA</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-left">
                <div><strong>Montant arrêté à :</strong> {{ vente.total|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} FCFA</div>
                <div>Document généré automatiquement par le système de gestion de la Clinique Médicale Nassarawa.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-right">
                <div class="qr">
                    {% set _qr = qr_data is defined ? qr_data : (verifyUrl is defined ? verifyUrl : null) %}
                    {% if _qr %}
                        <img src="{{ _qr }}" alt="QR Code">
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if code_qr is defined and code_qr %}
                        <small>Code : {{ code_qr }}</small>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if verifyUrl is defined and verifyUrl %}
                        <small><a href="{{ verifyUrl }}">{{ verifyUrl }}</a></small>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>

                <div class="sign">
                    <div class="sign-line">Signature / Cachet</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>